{"tid":840743,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"〔10年後metoo〕被指強姦 C朗告德國雜誌","createTime":"2018-09-29T04:49:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T06:03:52.000Z","uid":81562,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f2ad24fdd85fe66aac9b297df4e614fd5ef6237c","tid":840743,"uid":81562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T04:49:19.000Z","msg":"屌你老味 C朗都要強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又一隻臭雞自願爬上人床 十年後又反悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp23038283626\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp23038283626&d=F9r2SQMCT6%2FOx%2BzmKK%2FXAJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=5149ab07\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Fsports%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3Dsp23038283626&h=8ee170d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/sports/player?newsId=sp23038283626</a><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=F9r2SQMCT6%2FOx%2BzmKK%2FXAJWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=c40708e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】德國雜誌《明鏡周刊》指祖雲達斯球星基斯坦奴朗拿度於2009年時在拉斯維加斯強姦美國女子Kathryn Mayorga，C朗的律師將會控告該間德國雜誌。<br />\n<br />\n現年34歲的美國女子Kathryn Mayorga周五首次公開宣稱祖雲達斯球星基斯坦奴朗拿度，於2009年時在拉斯維加斯強姦她，而《明鏡周刊》更引述Kathryn Mayorga的律師史杜華爾，指C朗為女方提供了28萬7000鎊的掩口費。<br />\n<br />\n史杜華爾告訴《明鏡周刊》，他已代表Kathryn Mayorga提出民事訴訟，要求宣佈保密協議無效。史杜華爾說，「起訴的目的是讓基斯坦奴朗拿度在民事法庭上，要他對Kathryn Mayorga造成的傷害及後果負責。」<br />\n<br />\nC朗的律師史卓特茲在路透社的一份聲明中表示，雙方是在互相同意下發生關係，而《明鏡周刊》的報道是「在私隱領域不可接受的報道」，他將要求《明鏡周刊》賠償「相應於侵權嚴重程度的精神損害賠償」。<br />\n<br />\n史卓特茲說：「這可能是近年來最嚴重的侵犯個人權利行為之一。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : 互聯網"},{"pid":"7c550a4da803fbe3798de8f387db9ec3fea4fffe","tid":840743,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T04:50:21.000Z","msg":"kobe都要啦 有時食開easy野 想要d挑戰唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"126b88cb1cb204916128628e43d5114e91403e34","tid":840743,"uid":12565,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:27:02.000Z","msg":"屌你老味比晒錢安心玩<br />\n跟著n 年後就屈鳩人強姦話啲錢叫掩口費<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f25a9ec7e61a49ccacda29bf00e1c49db4e83d","tid":840743,"uid":76310,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:38:03.000Z","msg":"真心講<br />\n大把女自願比阿朗上<br />\n而且講比比錢，阿朗都唔會咁姑寒，仲捐錢都大把錢,點會計較<br />\n<br />\n有人反悔機會大d"},{"pid":"f5898fbd6144f08ce5d7707bc4ec871da72a6037","tid":840743,"uid":166434,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:42:50.000Z","msg":"死賤雞自殺啦"},{"pid":"66acba06e7e2a0c0424117a931492d8dd330d1c8","tid":840743,"uid":22535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66f25a9ec7e61a49ccacda29bf00e1c49db4e83d","tid":840743,"uid":76310,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:38:03.000Z","msg":"真心講<br />\n大把女自願比阿朗上<br />\n而且講比比錢，阿朗都唔會咁姑寒，仲捐錢都大把錢,點會計較<br />\n<br />\n有人反悔機會大d"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:44:31.000Z","msg":"作多筆姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34538c9fa80d16217e881be3834bb040d52363d6","tid":840743,"uid":53524,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:44:35.000Z","msg":"<pre><code data-type=\"\">史杜華爾，指C朗為女方提供了28萬7000鎊的掩口費。 \n史杜華爾說，「起訴的目的是讓基斯坦奴朗拿度在民事法庭上，要他對Kathryn Mayorga造成的傷害及後果負責。」</code></pre><br />\n俾錢壓傷左?"},{"pid":"84497715e3beaa0cefda3ce7ed2cfdd4626744b4","tid":840743,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-29T05:49:16.000Z","msg":"28萬7000鎊<br />\n<br />\n屌你班死臭雞又食又拎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d5651f3cafe46c54b42ca6c379c